sudah pergi, satunya lagi mau pergi.

107
00:11:40,766 --> 00:11:42,034
Barang-barang bagaimana?

108
00:11:42,235 --> 00:11:45,271
Oh, kau tahu. Tinggal beberapa
peti kemas terakhir.

109
00:11:45,404 --> 00:11:49,542
2400 ton kargo komersil,
200 ton bantuan makanan.

110
00:11:49,709 --> 00:11:54,714
