Ya ampun.

153
00:15:28,694 --> 00:15:29,995
Sampai jumpa di bawah, Mike.

154
00:15:46,378 --> 00:15:49,381
Rute utama mereka dipenuhi kapal...

155
00:15:50,916 --> 00:15:53,619
...tapi kita tak bisa menyerang kawanan.

156
00:15:59,992 --> 00:16:02,962
